Point density.description: A freedraw object has many points. Converting freedraw to a line with too many points will result in an impractical object that is hard to edit. This setting sepcifies how many points from freedraw should be averaged to form a point on the line

Layout Options JSON.description: You can use layout options to configure the layout algorithm. A list of all options and further details of their exact effects is available in ELK's documentation.
